From 106b926cda2af7dbf9a41bce9b5bc9bb423aac5e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dariusz Majnert <dariusz@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 00:57:53 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] emc: add resumable Stop for active AUTO programs

Add a dedicated task and trajectory Stop operation that preserves interpreter and motion queues. Stop safely completes position-synchronized motion, snapshots spindle and coolant outputs, and gates Resume on spindle at-speed inputs. Expose the command and Stop state through Python and HALUI; Node bindings are maintained in the consumer repository.
