new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..fbf9cdddb6
--- /dev/null
+++ b/tests/resumable-stop/README
@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@
+Verify resumable Stop preserves an active AUTO program and resumes it.
+
+This regression test exercises the task-level Stop operation directly through
+the Python command API. It checks that an active feed move stops without
+aborting queued AUTO state, that spindle and coolant outputs are disabled
+while stopped, and that Resume restores them before continuing the same
+program to completion.
